header.title: Women and Ageism - Are You Proud of Your Age?
header.subtitle: NA
header.postText: 'I love the age question. I love topics that make people squirm. And I think it's fascinating the lengths that some women, and many men, will go through to deny that they are -- gasp! -- actually getting older.. . 'She's old, though, isn't she?' a young girl asked me with the same inflection that she might have voiced, 'Oh, but she had a terrible accident, didn't she?' about one of the most powerful editors in New York.'*. . Are women scared to admit their age because of presumed prejudice? Is ageism a real concern? Mandy at XOjane says she's more confident than ever at 37; do you feel more confident now than when you were in your 'prime?' Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, and Wes Clark Jr. (consultant, veteran) break it down. . . *Read more from Mandy at XOjane:. https://www.xojane.com/beauty/botox-i.... .
